{"tid":2261585,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[睇書]有冇人睇開社會心理學書籍","createTime":"2020-10-28T12:14:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T14:40:56.000Z","uid":243691,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ab815915fb0a9fa88b0f7fada3aa35b29980002e","tid":2261585,"uid":243691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T12:14:53.000Z","msg":"情緒低潮，有心理問題既時候，睇雞湯會帶比你一時振奮同鼓勵，相信廣大既連登仔都可以寫本書出黎。<br />\n但係睇心理學既書往往會提供一條更好既出路，建立全面既觀念同知識，解決問題。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有四本書想推介下　相信博學多才既連登仔會睇過 可以討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望有睇開書既巴打都可以推薦下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然係簡體，但係內容係唔錯，如果唔想睇殘體可以睇番英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n《社會性動物》　The Social Animal<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.haodoo.net/covers/13C4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.haodoo.net%2Fcovers%2F13C4.jpg&h=204a5767&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《社會心理學》　Social Psychology<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.kknews.cc/SIG=m2e356/p05000o5s742qp24707.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3Dm2e356%2Fp05000o5s742qp24707.jpg&h=9e6b4579&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《影響力》 influence the psychology of persuasion<br />\n<img src=\"https://im2.book.com.tw/image/getImage?i=https://www.books.com.tw/img/001/049/57/0010495733.jpg&amp;v=4d5a5715&amp;w=348&amp;h=348\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fim2.book.com.tw%2Fimage%2FgetImage%3Fi%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.books.com.tw%2Fimg%2F001%2F049%2F57%2F0010495733.jpg%26v%3D4d5a5715%26w%3D348%26h%3D348&h=054a49bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《態度改變與社會影響》the psychology of attitude change and social influence<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/SIG=1h6rh8d/ctp-vzntr/15267958307928oro3n9oso.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D1h6rh8d%2Fctp-vzntr%2F15267958307928oro3n9oso.jpg&h=1baea4bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n頭三本都好易入口，趣味性較高，如果對社會群體現象，從眾，群眾心理有興趣可以入手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第四本學術性較高，亦比其他三本知名度較低，但係一本最全面既社會心理學書，容易引起思考，基本上係難讀既一本書，但係非常好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望有其他巴打可以推薦下其他書<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3886451c45bd8f8e8cce9983566899d5ba7702fc","tid":2261585,"uid":295230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T12:29:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RFuJF51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRFuJF51.jpg&h=b8d8e388&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"18a213c96013b78ad13aafb6150161d799e8be87","tid":2261585,"uid":25194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T12:35:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0e66ea01199b674c31bf765f439d043cf7b22ce","tid":2261585,"uid":371746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3886451c45bd8f8e8cce9983566899d5ba7702fc","tid":2261585,"uid":295230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T12:29:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RFuJF51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRFuJF51.jpg&h=b8d8e388&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T12:48:20.000Z","msg":"哇本書嘅繁中版係咁嘅"},{"pid":"f97ec0278970ad98ff241e6bbcee6d431076c7c1","tid":2261585,"uid":243691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T13:25:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f586840f340ad57286c149b24fe8d2a55aad8120","tid":2261585,"uid":30831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0e66ea01199b674c31bf765f439d043cf7b22ce","tid":2261585,"uid":371746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3886451c45bd8f8e8cce9983566899d5ba7702fc","t